\pard\qc\sa180\b\fs28 10. RESULTS AND DISCUSSION\b0\fs22\par
\par
\pard\sa120\b 10.1 Severity Model Metrics (Latest Run)\b0\par
\par
\pard | Model | CV Macro-F1 | Test Accuracy | Test Macro-F1 | Test Macro-Recall |\par
\pard |---|---:|---:|---:|---:|\par
\pard | XGBoost | 0.3412 | 0.7273 | 0.3821 | 0.3779 |\par
\pard | CatBoost | 0.2942 | 0.7619 | 0.3282 | 0.3518 |\par
\pard | RandomForest | 0.2928 | 0.7532 | 0.3070 | 0.3388 |\par
\par
